messages: 1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (17:55): God doesn't want me to do something...
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (17:57): But I can tell you what god is doing to stop me...
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (17:58): I can't do it on wednesday...
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (17:58): ...so he doesn't make anything that day...
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (17:59): ...I could do it today, but he made me run out of money...
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (17:59): ...I could do it tomorrow, but I will leave work too early...
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (18:00): ...I could do it on Saturday, Sunday or Monday...
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (18:01): ...But I don't know if i can manage to leave work at time...
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (18:01): ...I could do it on wednesday, but...
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (18:02): And those were the only days i could do it...
cb4f671d94c55be0649c821768f00da4 (18:02): If anything simply cannot go wrong, it will anyway.
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (18:03): If something has a 50-50 possibility of go wron or right
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (18:03): It has a 90% of going wrong
cb4f671d94c55be0649c821768f00da4 (18:03): Just when you think things cannot get any worse, they will.
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (18:06): I could have done it today...
cb4f671d94c55be0649c821768f00da4 (18:07): So, do it tomorrow. Or we can do it together.
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (18:08): Beacause you mustn't know about the nature of my affair
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (18:09): Only my two comrades, or one of them, can do that with me.
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (18:09): And they don't even know what is it.
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (18:09): They only know a place and a time.
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (18:11): If you come at 13:25 GMT+1 hour.
cb4f671d94c55be0649c821768f00da4 (18:15): Unlucky me. I'm not in Spain.
1384011d72c6ea4e15ad6205cc695486 (18:16): Then, I won't wait for you.
